informalexample.programlisting:
Get all resources (os auth owner user. Admin sees all resources) GET http://localhost:13000/baker/services/api/repo/admin/subscribedresources/
Get a resource GET http://localhost:13000/baker/services/api/repo/admin/subscribedresources/12
Add a resource POST http://localhost:13000/baker/services/api/repo/admin/subscribedresources/ example payload: {"owner":{"id":34,"organization":"dev","name":"dev","email":"dev@dev.gr","username":"dev","password":"53mJ7SF1jngzGyDkd/xVgg==","role":"ROLE_DEVELOPER","active":false,"currentSessionID":"214f663c-de06-418f-8e75-156d53fe5d13"},"url":"192.168.1.2"}

	
	
